data.description: Welcome to 21011 Willows Drive, an exceptional property located in the desirable area of Willow Woods Lexington Park. As the former model home for Willow Woods, this stunning detached home offers spacious living, and a large corner fenced in yard making it the perfect place to call home. With a generous 1,844 square feet of floorspace, this unit boasts ample room for all your needs. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by new flooring throughout a functional floor plan. The main level features a well-appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances, as well as a cozy living room with gas fireplace where you can relax and unwind after a long day. The unit offers four generously sized bedrooms, providing plenty of space for family and guests. The two and a half bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy for everyone. Additionally, this property comes with ample room for all your vehicles. Home has been well maintained with New HVAC unit, New Roof and New flooring throughout. Located in Lexington Park, you'll enjoy easy access to a range of amenities including shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment options. Commuting is a breeze with convenient access to NAS Patuxent River Naval Base, major highways and transportation routes. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own this beautiful home. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the lifestyle that awaits you at 21011 Willows Drive.
